<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-28-0509 </DOCNO><TEXT>The second generation of a microcomputer software program PCTRAN, PCTRAN-2,has been expanded to simulate containment and fuel conditions in additionto reactor coolant parameters. Since all major areas of safety concernare included, it can be used for emergency planning at a nuclear powerplant. In this paper, its use in generating emergency drill scenariosis discussed.</TEXT></DOC>